- No. You are a spy like me.

13
00:00:35,160 --> 00:00:36,620
- 這是… - 是你
That's... You.

14
00:00:37,080 --> 00:00:40,560
如果我回家 他們會找到我 只有阻止他們 我才能保護家人
If I go home, they're gonna find me. Stopping them, that's how I protect my family.

15
00:00:40,760 --> 00:00:43,020
