Private mode initiated.

19
00:00:48,010 --> 00:00:49,580
貨物怎么樣了

20
00:00:49,950 --> 00:00:52,040
- 她還知道什么  - 她知道的并不多
What else did she know? Not a lot.

21
00:00:52,540 --> 00:00:55,200
我們會把事情搞定 然后我就回你身邊
We're gonna figure this out, and then I'm coming back to you, okay?

22
00:00:55,620 --> 00:00:57,100
- 跟我聊聊他吧 - 誰
Tell me about him. - Who?

23
00:00:57,300 --> 00:00:58,310
梅森 他是什么樣的人
- Mason, who was he?

24
00:00:58,510 --> 00:01:00,310
沒辦法跟你說 我跟他關系沒那么近
Couldn't tell you. We weren't that close.

25
00:01:00,510 --> 00:01:02,200
- 從來沒有私人交情 - 從來沒有
- We never got personal. - Never?

26
00:01:04,000 --> 00:01:07,850
凱恩 我很驚訝 你居然會愛上一個
I am surprised, Kane, that you, of all people,

27
00:01:08,050 --> 00:01:10,650
曾經摧毀了堡壘的女人
would carry a torch for the woman who brought Citadel to its knees.

28
00:01:10,840 --> 00:01:12,190
數據傳輸完成 趕快出來
Transfer's complete. Get out of there.

29
00:01:12,390 --> 00:01:13,600
你到底在說什么
The hell are you talking about?

30
00:01:13,800 --> 00:01:14,770
是你的女友 納迪亞
It was your girl Nadia.

31
00:01:14,970 --> 00:01:15,830
是你嗎
Was it you?

32
00:01:17,000 --> 00:01:18,440
這是布瑞爾 對吧
That's Brielle, right?

33
00:01:18,640 --> 00:01:19,730
你愛的女人
The woman you love,

34
00:01:19,930 --> 00:01:20,940
她還活著
she's alive.

35
00:01:21,140 --> 00:01:21,900
不會吧
- No.

36
00:01:22,090 --> 00:01:23,060
她叫艾比
- Her name is Abby,

37
00:01:23,260 --> 00:01:25,000
她嫁給了梅森凱恩
and she's married to Mason Kane.

38
00:01:25,870 --> 00:01:28,810
我是特工卡特斯賓塞
This is Agent Carter Spence.

39
00:01:29,010 --> 00:01:30,980
曼提柯爾正在接近我的位置
Manticore's closing in on my location.

40
00:01:31,180 --> 00:01:32,730
這可能是我最后一次通訊
This might be my last transmission.

41
00:01:32,930 --> 00:01:33,870
媽的
Shit.

42
00:01:34,830 --> 00:01:35,950
我知道他在哪
I know where he is.

43
00:01:47,080 --> 00:01:49,830
摩洛哥

44
